from the youth system...

207
00:12:44.096 --> 00:12:46.033
It was like a jigsaw puzzle.

208
00:12:46.068 --> 00:12:50.324
Jimmy Murphy was with him.
His number two was with him.

209
00:12:50.326 --> 00:12:52.726
We gelled. We gelled.

210
